flowchart TD
    A[User Message Received] --> B{Match against skill<br/>description triggers?}

    B -->|No match| C[Handle as general<br/>conversation]
    B -->|Match found| D[Select best-matching skill]

    D --> E[Level 1: Metadata<br/>Always in context]
    E --> F["Load name + description<br/>(~100 words from YAML frontmatter)"]

    F --> G[Level 2: Skill Body<br/>Loaded on trigger]
    G --> H["Load SKILL.md body<br/>(≤3000 words, imperative instructions)"]

    H --> I{Does skill need<br/>supplementary context?}

    I -->|No| J[Execute skill with<br/>body instructions only]

    I -->|Yes| K[Level 3: Bundled Resources<br/>Loaded on demand]
    K --> L["Load references/*.md<br/>(unlimited size, detailed docs)"]
    K --> M["Load examples/*<br/>(working code samples)"]
    K --> N["Load scripts/*<br/>(utility scripts)"]

    L --> J
    M --> J
    N --> J

    J --> O{Skill references<br/>~~connectors?}
    O -->|Yes| P{MCP servers<br/>connected?}
    O -->|No| Q[Generate output<br/>from instructions alone]

    P -->|Connected| R[Supercharged Mode:<br/>Fetch data from MCPs]
    P -->|Not connected| S[Standalone Mode:<br/>Ask user for input]

    R --> T[Structured Response]
    S --> T
    Q --> T
